# Spec 0048 — greedy serving for the bake-off's reproducibility precondition.
# temperature=0 makes the explorer's single draw reproducible (validated: the
# non-greedy qwen3:14b flipped empty<->right-file-wrong-span across two runs of
# astropy-12907; the greedy variant reproduced identically, tool-count and all).
# The explorer sends only {max_tokens: 2048} (0034/0038 byte-pin), so greedy MUST
# be a server-side default here — it cannot be injected per-request.
FROM qwen3:14b
PARAMETER temperature 0
PARAMETER top_p 1
PARAMETER seed 0
